    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, always kept it garaged, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for the road, this is the one. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
