    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-quality masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and fragrant, showing absolutely no bolster wear or sun fading. Every button functions with tactile precision, and the infotainment screen is crystal clear. Mechanically, it is flawless; a comprehensive service history is provided, documenting every routine fluid change and preventative maintenance milestone. From the pristine, dust-free engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful, offering a truly 'new car' experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than the best.",
      "price": 46500.0,
