      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels just like it rolled off the lot yesterday! I've taken such good care of it, always kept it tucked away in the garage and treated it like a member of the family. It drives like a total dream and is ready for a brand-new home. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the crazy dealership sticker shock, this is the one! Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
