    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS system. This unit has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the structural and internal integrity of the chassis. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power to a factory limited-slip differential. Every bushing and damper has been inspected to maintain the original M-division kinematics. The paint is flawless, reflecting its climate-controlled storage history. A mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
